A Study of the Enchantedness of Coincidence.

The fascination regarding the clash of opposites goes back to antiquity. The ancient poets extolled its inherent beauty.

The attraction of opposing natures has always encouraged the simmering of synergies and the subsequent birth of something new and extraordinary.

Herein Lies the Magic of Accident.

Three fragrances, three worlds of bewitching collisions.
